msgctxt "84_Hostess-Lovin' CEO"
msgid "Did Elise hire a new girl? That's what I heard, but I don't know if it's true."
msgstr "¿Escuchaste que el Elise contrató a una chica nueva? No sé si sea verdad."

msgctxt "96_Lower-Ranking Employee"
msgid "They did, they did! Her name's Lily. She's a bit older than the other girls, but I think that's actually a plus!"
msgstr "¡Sí, es verdad! Se llama Lily. ¡Es mayor que las demás, pero creo que eso le da un punto a favor!"

msgctxt "108_Hostess-Lovin' CEO"
msgid "Really? Is she that good?"
msgstr "¿De verdad? ¿Tan buena es?"

msgctxt "120_Lower-Ranking Employee"
msgid "Yeah! She's cute and sexy at the same time. Just seeing her drives me crazy! Let's get in there and request her!"
msgstr "¡Sí! Es linda y sexy a la vez. ¡Con solo verla me vuelvo loco! ¡Entremos y solicitemosla!"

